{"id": 550, "genre": 1001, "title": "你最糟的海淘体验是什么？", "description": "跨越千年的等待。", "record_count": 3522, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183614JuS8wWCOhf7LVdi1.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-03T01:09:40Z", "options": [{"id": 14848, "content": "等待时间长，其他都挺赞。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 226972}, {"id": 15108, "content": "看着有点担心我的表", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182750pO2nsPSgE5ifJaNl.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231481}, {"id": 14600, "content": "转运公司每单必报，且运费怎么会怎么算。然后一个月后才寄出……心塞到死！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223846}, {"id": 14602, "content": "我无话可说，因为我一般都是去商店买的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223894}, {"id": 15629, "content": "包被邮政退回，重新发货需要运费和增值税，还不能全款退货，只能磨着性子慢慢等，一点脾气都没有〒_〒", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236387}, {"id": 14350, "content": "费老大劲买回来发现某猫某东活动特价，海淘买回来的比国内的还要贵好多钱。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 352, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211409}, {"id": 14351, "content": "运丢了??", "image": null, "praise_count": 180, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211409}, {"id": 15631, "content": "沒有信用卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236385}, {"id": 14355, "content": "买了Herschel的包包等了N久 最后等到的是海关通知书。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 183136}, {"id": 14611, "content": "转运到中国的时候遇上了EMS", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163987}, {"id": 14612, "content": "海淘是什么鬼？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223729}, {"id": 14359, "content": "本来想抢个首发  一个月发货 一个月过海关 还被税", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197855}, {"id": 14872, "content": "海淘38码的美貌凉鞋，老公穿正好?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227470}, {"id": 15640, "content": "看准了特价优惠买的东西，结果发现平时的价格更低", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227367}, {"id": 16152, "content": "cghd", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225462}, {"id": 14362, "content": "淘了一位越南新娘，过关的时候，老爷说，都得“睡”………………", "image": null, "praise_count": 101, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219821}, {"id": 14365, "content": "国卡加转运地址根本过不了，连后续问题都没有可能遇到，难道不是最悲催？", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219837}, {"id": 14623, "content": "莫名的快递，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224191}, {"id": 14368, "content": "根本就没收到货～然后...心塞塞???", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219931}, {"id": 14370, "content": "一星期退换货3次?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202128}, {"id": 14626, "content": "被税了…税金是商品价格的一半…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224288}, {"id": 16162, "content": "令人心碎的运费", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241901}, {"id": 14371, "content": "买了眼药水，寄到学校的，结果包裹外面写的是润滑液！", "image": null, "praise_count": 204, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201950}, {"id": 15651, "content": "到家就过期了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236605}, {"id": 14628, "content": "运回来的东西，变质了，还不知道找谁", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224392}, {"id": 14629, "content": "复活节买的端午节礼物中秋节才到", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224412}, {"id": 15653, "content": "一二个月还在等", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236575}, {"id": 15657, "content": "海淘两次 海关清关两次-_-#", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235809}, {"id": 15914, "content": "15215588093", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237420}, {"id": 14379, "content": "被税了，还被告知: 如果只买一件商品就会被认为是自用。可惜手痒买了两样。更可气的，税费的基数还是货值+国际快递费，因为没有标明货值是CIF，就被默认FOB，你妹的～ 凸..凸", "image": null, "praise_count": 109, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 882894}, {"id": 14898, "content": "海淘是什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228179}, {"id": 15410, "content": "给了评价卖家不理你！死活叫不出来，呵呵哒", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229380}, {"id": 14387, "content": "抢了半天兴冲冲付款发现运费比购物车一半东西都贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 125, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 14388, "content": "别人都开始找bug了，我的6s还没开始发货，我是第一天抢的啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157780}, {"id": 16180, "content": "等太久", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242185}, {"id": 14389, "content": "厕所门口等别人拉完屎", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219315}, {"id": 14901, "content": "看到这个话题我才想起来我三个月前海淘的东西到现在还没到，消息都没有-_-||", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228257}, {"id": 14390, "content": "淘宝买过一次衣服。拿到就后悔了。不说了。说多了都是眼泪啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194834}, {"id": 14391, "content": "从前有个叫做日拍迷妹必备的东西 一逛就停不下来 拼老命和樱花妹竞拍！高价拍来出都出不掉???", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202394}, {"id": 14392, "content": "买回来的电器用不了。而你压根不知道是因为电压差异弄坏的还是它本身就是坏的……远在大洋彼岸的保修也就是浮云～", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141800}, {"id": 14904, "content": "买完发现降价", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 226414}, {"id": 14393, "content": "买好了可是运到了别人家", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 176963}, {"id": 14397, "content": "真不想提，一提全是泪，住在比利时，在日亚购物被税150欧，东西第二天就坏了，再寄回日本又被税90美元，然后和日亚磨了三个月的嘴皮子才把钱退给我T_T ", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, 